<article id="post-264" class="post-264 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-66 tag-67">
	<header class="entry-header">
			<h1 class="entry-title">更新一篇最近学会的“科学上网”</h1>
		<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on">Posted on <a href="https://www.stephenlearn.com/archives/264" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-03-14T20:23:01+00:00">2018年3月14日</time><time class="updated" datetime="2018-03-14T20:24:42+00:00">2018年3月14日</time></a></span><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://www.stephenlearn.com/archives/author/admin_f">stephen</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="https://www.stephenlearn.com/archives/264#respond">Leave a comment</a></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<h2><a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shadowsocks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shadowsocks</a> 是什么</h2>
<p>Shadowsocks 是一种安全的 socks5 代理，可以保护你的上网流量。基于多种加密方式，推荐使用 aes-256-cfb 加密。安装和使用需要本地端和服务端。本地客户端已经包含了多种版本，包括iOS，Android，Windows，MAC，甚至是路由器 (基于OpenWRT)，所以使用方便，各取所需。</p>
<p><em>远程服务端则一般安装在基于 Linux 的各种发行版操作系统，比如 Debian， CentOS， Fedora， Redhat， Ubuntu， openSUSE等。</em></p>
<h2>Shadowsocks 的作者是谁</h2>
<p>最初只有 Python 版，由 @clowwindy 开发和维护，后来随着知名度提高，开始出现各种语言的版本，其中比较知名的是 libev ， go， nodejs 等版本，需要注意的是，nodejs 的作者也是 @clowwindy，但最近已不再维护该版本。libev 的维护者是 @madeye，长期更新。具体请查看<a href="https://shadowsocks.org/en/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网</a>。</p>
<h2>一键脚本</h2>
<p>先把这位前辈的SSR一键脚本放这里<a href="https://doub.io/ss-jc42/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">『原创』ShadowsocksR 单/多端口 一键管理脚本</a>。</p>
<p>还有这位前辈的<a href="https://www.bennythink.com/shadowsocks.html" data-slimstat="5">Shadowsocks 介绍、搭建及使用简明教程</a>。</p>
<p>有需要的可以自取。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>但在这里我要说的是。。。。</p>
<h2>SS原版安装</h2>
<p>地址先放这~Github：<a href="https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks/tree/master" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks/tree/master</a></p>
<h3>安装</h3>
<p>Debian / Ubuntu:</p>
<pre><code>apt-get install python-pip
pip install git+https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks.git@master
</code></pre>
<p>CentOS:</p>
<pre><code>yum install python-setuptools &amp;&amp; easy_install pip
pip install git+https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks.git@master
</code></pre>
<h3>运行</h3>
<pre><code>ssserver -p 443 -k password -m aes-256-cfb
</code></pre>
<p>后台运行:</p>
<pre><code>sudo ssserver -p 443 -k password -m aes-256-cfb --user nobody -d start
</code></pre>
<p>后台结束:</p>
<pre><code>sudo ssserver -d stop
</code></pre>
<p>查看日志:</p>
<pre><code>sudo tailf /var/log/shadowsocks.log
</code></pre>
<p>如果嫌麻烦请右转<a href="https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks/wiki/Configuration-via-Config-File" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Configuration-via-Config-File</a>。</p>
<p>利用配置文件运行。</p>
<p>新建 <code>/etc/shadowsocks.json</code>内容如下：</p>
<pre><code>{
    "server":"0.0.0.0",
    "server_port":8388,
    "local_address": "127.0.0.1",
    "local_port":1080,
    "password":"mypassword",
    "timeout":300,
    "method":"aes-256-cfb",
    "fast_open": false
}</code></pre>
<p>前台运行:</p>
<pre><code>ssserver -c /etc/shadowsocks.json
</code></pre>
<p>后台运行:</p>
<pre><code>ssserver -c /etc/shadowsocks.json -d start
ssserver -c /etc/shadowsocks.json -d stop</code></pre>
<p><code>看到这么长一段运行命令，表示很无奈。（可以使用alias，简化它。）</code></p>
<pre><code>alias ssserverstart='ssserver -c /etc/shadowsocks.json -d start'
alias ssserverstop='ssserver -c /etc/shadowsocks.json -d stop’</code></pre>
<h2>瘟斗士：</h2>
<p>下载地址：<a href="https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-windows/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-windows/releases</a></p>
<p>界面如下，删除未配置的服务器。输入服务器地址，端口，密码和加密方式。</p>
<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-265" src="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/windos-300x287.png" alt="科学上网" width="300" height="287" srcset="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/windos-300x287.png 300w, https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/windos.png 477w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p>默认使用PAC代理。</p>
<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-266" src="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/windos1-300x199.png" alt="" width="300" height="199" srcset="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/windos1-300x199.png 300w, https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/windos1.png 400w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p>也可以下载扩展，如Chrome的SwitchySharp 新建一个情景模式：</p>
<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-267" src="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/windos3-300x241.png" alt="科学上网" width="300" height="241" srcset="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/windos3-300x241.png 300w, https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/windos3.png 573w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<p>也可以使用系统代理和全局代理。</p>
<h2 id="title-4">Android：</h2>
<p>去 Google Play 搜索 <a title="" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.github.shadowsocks" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-original-title="" data-slimstat="5">shadowsocks</a>，下载安装，之后遵循如下步骤：</p>
<p>右上角 + 号，手动设置，添加配置文件，写入对应的 IP、端口、密码、加密方式，</p>
<p>路由中有 7 个选项，推荐设置成<strong>GFW列表</strong>，也就是无法访问的走代理、其他直连。</p>
<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-276" src="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/IMG_20180314_201451-169x300.jpg" alt="科学上网" width="169" height="300" srcset="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/IMG_20180314_201451-169x300.jpg 169w, https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/IMG_20180314_201451-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/IMG_20180314_201451-576x1024.jpg 576w, https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/IMG_20180314_201451.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 169px) 100vw, 169px" /></p>
<h2>IOS：</h2>
<p>去 App Store 购买 shadowrocket、surge 等工具，然后大概就是添加呗，很简单的啊。看图吧。</p>
<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-278" src="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ios-1-300x199.jpg" alt="科学上网" width="300" height="199" srcset="https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ios-1-300x199.jpg 300w, https://www.stephenlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ios-1.jpg 548w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
